entries.femaleVariant: Hey, V... I was thinking about you the other day and I thought I'd just, well... give you a call.
Hey, V.
Umm... Hey, V.
Pick up, pick up, pick--
Hey, V!
I know it's pointless, but... once upon a time people were talking to graves and nobody batted an eyelid, right?
When I said I was thinking about you, I meant A LOT. 'Bout everything you did.
And... I guess... I get it – why you wanted to leave this place once and for all.
But s-- still, V... pheww... Did you even think about, y'know – what happens when--
I... Shit, I can't do this...
I'm just, uh... I'm callin' to say goodbye.
I've finally decided to up and leave this city for good.
I realized this place only gives you two choices – you either become an asshole, or eventually you get offed by one.
I hope... you somehow find an alternative.
It's just a shame things had to end this way.
Have a nice life, V.
I was just wonderin' how you've been... haven't heard from you in a while. Still livin' large in Night City?
I dunno... All I think about is droppin' everything and leaving, and yet here I am, still...
This city's like quicksand, the more you try to get out, the more it pulls you in.
Once you're up to your knees, you're never gettin' out, like... like Evelyn.
Anyway, look out for yourself, OK? And call me sometime. Bye.
Fuck!
V... I-I don't know where we went wrong... maybe something happened, or you needed to lay low...
If you can just give me s-some kinda signal that... that you're alive and everything's OK... please...
If you ever need help, you know I'm here for you, right? Always.
Long time no see! Lemme guess – you still the top of your game in all of Night City? Heheh, yeah, I left all that.
I guess I'm just callin' to say thanks – for everything. Wasn't until I'd left everything behind that I realized how depressed I was for all that time.
Take it from me, V, if you ever get the chance... just leave. Leave and don't look back. The weight it takes of your shoulders, I... I can't even describe it.
All right, 'nuff lecturing. Take it easy, girl.
entries.maleVariant: All right, 'nuff lecturing. Take it easy, man.

entries.femaleVariant: Stay safe... and call me when you hear this.
